	default y
	bool "Support for Ramdump"
	depends on ARCH_R8A7373
	help
	  This enables ramdump feature. It will flush caches from oops,panic
	  and emerg kmsg callback. It will also save exceptio, core&mmu and
	  some hw registers to ram.

